@nisdas I don't think it's a hardware or performance problem, I've run the node on an i7 and even on an i3 with 32GB ram and a 4TB fast nvme, I haven't had any problems before either.

The MEVBoost 1.6.0 update was released 2 weeks ago and I have been Missing since before.

Thanks

@Ololosha100501 are you running the latest prysm version?

Unfortunately I had to migrate to Lighthouse (rust client) after being a validator with prysm for over 2 years.

Since I migrated, no more missed proposals, and running the same mev-boost 1.6.. I was having 100% rate of missed blocks
